description: Three gutsy kids from a rapidly gentrifying Bronx neighborhood stumble upon a sinister plot to suck all the life from their beloved community.

title: Green Room
cast: Anton Yelchin, Imogen Poots, Patrick Stewart, Alia Shawkat, Joe Cole, Callum Turner, Macon Blair, David W. Thompson, Mark Webber, Eric Edelstein, Kai Lennox
description: At the end of their low-budget tour, a punk band accepts a gig at an isolated rural club, only to discover that their hosts are neo-Nazis.

title: Secret Magic Control Agency
cast: Nicholas Corda, Sylvana Joyce, Alyson Leigh Rosenfeld, Courtney Shaw, Erica Schroeder, Georgette Timoney, Mary O'Brady, Marc Thompson
description: Hansel and Gretel of fairy tale fame — now acting as secret agents — must use magic, clever thinking and teamwork on a mission to find a missing king.
